title: Christmas Wish #14: The Hermes-Bakken Family
description: Carole nominated her neighbor Chase and him family.  Their landlord is kicking them out because he's selling the place but in the meantime, their rent raised $350 a month.  They've adopted two children and are trying their best to find a new place to live.
